##合算
scoreboard players operation $Def _1 *= $Def _2
scoreboard players set $Def _2 100
scoreboard players operation $Def _1 /= $Def _2
scoreboard players operation $Def _1 /= $Def _2
scoreboard players operation $Def _1 *= $Def _3
